This paper is about a type system for constraint logic programs, which is a subfield of programming languages (cs.PL). The paper also discusses the subject reduction property, which is a topic in logic (cs.LO). Additionally, the paper focuses on detecting programming errors statically, which is a concern in software engineering (cs.SE) and artificial intelligence (cs.AI). Finally, the paper mentions the implementation of the system for type checking and type inference, which involves formal methods and programming languages (cs.FL).
